        <h1>Med Spa SEO vs PPC: Which Actually Drives More Patients in Miami (2026)</h1>
        <p class="lead">Most Miami med spas waste budget by picking the wrong channel for the wrong stage. Here's the honest math on SEO versus Google Ads, when each one wins, when to run both, and what a working Miami budget actually looks like.</p>
